{
  "stem": "26022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was only one bed in that single cell, which was sort of flipped up towards the wall, and that was flipped down, and that was given to the oldest person.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the oldest person was a Jehovah's Witness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And over her bed was a shelf.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here I am, being pushed in and no place to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they pushed me in the door, and I was standing at the door because I couldn't take a step.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, it was dusk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there I was standing, and this woman on the bed slowly reaches up to the shelf, puts in her teeth and says, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] are you Jewish?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I say, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these women on the floor got very, very active, very busy, very excited, because they were not going to have a Jew person there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the woman on the shelf-- on that bed-- said-- the Jehovah's Witness said-- let her be.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are also human.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One more time when my life was saved.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That saved my life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This woman said I was human, so I was let be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was only one problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where am I going to be?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where am I going to spend the night?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, in the corner was an open john-- no seat, no cover, no nothing, just-- and I could be along-- since it was open, I couldn't even sit on it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I could slide alongside at the wall with my knees thrown up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where I spent the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Except if somebody had to use the john, they would yank up their skirt and go to the john.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The skirt would fall over me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I don't know what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
